{"blogid": "124092480", "writerAge": "码龄5年", "writerBlogNum": "107", "writerCollect": "130", "writerComment": "29", "writerFan": "22", "writerGrade": "5级", "writerIntegral": "2630", "writerName": "PlatoWG", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_124092480.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "38604", "writerRankWeekly": "48264", "writerThumb": "33", "writerVisitNum": "180203", "blog_read_count": "3799", "blog_time": "已于 2022-04-29 08:41:12 修改", "blog_title": "k8s多容器实现nginx+php-fpm", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-light\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<h1><a id=\"_0\"></a>背景</h1>\n<p>生产中总使用nginx+php的架构，在dockerhub上搜索都是nginx+php-fpm集合在一起的镜像，为了方便在k8s上方便的使用lnmp架构，并方便升级nginx或管理php插件，特总结此篇方便后期使用</p>\n<h1><a id=\"_2\"></a>实现思路</h1>\n<p>为了方便单独管理nginx和php，我通过多容器的思路来实现</p>\n<div class=\"mermaid sequence-diagram\">\n<svg height=\"343.890625\" id=\"mermaid-svg-hThhwqTXwdzGzIsb\" style=\"max-width: 450.5625px;\" viewbox=\"0 0 450.5625 343.890625\" width=\"100%\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<style>#mermaid-svg-hThhwqTXwdzGzIsb {font-family:\"trebuchet ms\",verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;fill:#333;}#mermaid-svg-hThhwqTXwdzGzIsb .error-icon{fill:#552222;}#mermaid-svg-hThhwqTXwdzGzIsb .error-text{fill:#552222;stroke:#552222;}#mermaid-svg-hThhwqTXwdzGzIsb .edge-thickness-normal{stroke-width:2px;}#mermaid-svg-hThhwqTXwdzGzIsb .edge-thickness-thick{stroke-width:3.5px;}#mermaid-svg-hThhwqTXwdzGzIsb .edge-pattern-solid{stroke-dasharray:0;}#mermaid-svg-hThhwqTXwdzGzIsb .edge-pattern-dashed{stroke-dasharray:3;}#mermaid-svg-hThhwqTXwdzGzIsb .edge-pattern-dotted{stroke-dasharray:2;}#me